
1. Install postgresql

2. Create a user and a database
sudo su postgres -c "createuser ocsimore"
sudo su postgres createdb ocsimore

3. Install pgocaml
http://merjis.com/developers/pgocaml

4. Compile ocsimore
make depend
make

5. Adapt your ocsigen.conf using ocsigen.conf.example
and run Ocsigen

